Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小空起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就站在镜子前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗姐  昨天也忙到很晚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会忙到晚上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭要给你留着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅儿真是样样能行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（松崎海，「海」在法语中读作「拉·梅尔（La Mer）」，\N梅儿是北斗为小海取的昵称）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个礼拜院里人手不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我袜子漏了一个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到缝纫机边上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的袜子总是漏洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不怪我  用不了几天就显得小了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小陆  这是你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  便当也多给我装一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够你吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小陆  我的煎蛋给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  北斗姐  你也得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道你们俩谁是当医生的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又倒那么多酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广小路姐  吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈的份就给小陆和广小路两个人分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆  要不要给您沏杯茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不急  等你都忙完的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家头发总是梳不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不梳就已经很漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗今天也很晚才回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这一份是广小路姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实习医生还真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:31.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（松崎  虞美人庄）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小海  要不要我送你一程？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗的衣服只要晾干一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哟  早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个  说的不就是梅儿你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会升信号旗的只有梅儿一个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拉丁广场周报\N坚决反对拆除  保护传统的拉丁广场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:36.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35}少女哟  你高高地升起信号旗\N为何\N你要将思念托付给清晨的海风\N在你所呼唤的远方\N却只被那随性的乌鸦所带走\N少女啊  此时\N那红白相间的\N那被深蓝色所包围的信号旗\N仍在迎风飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧  说的就是梅儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是松崎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像把漂流瓶扔进海里一样的行为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学部的怪人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野同学他也是拉丁广场的居民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（拉丁广场原指巴黎市学生聚集的拉丁区，带有一种文化的意味）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我占好桌子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天也好挤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:03.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}咖喱做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信子  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吃咖喱乌冬？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好  我就好这一口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠子你还不是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吃豆沙面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好  我就好这一口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅儿的便当还是这么丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信子你也自己做不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是想做的话  区区一份便当还不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？搞什么名堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二一二一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  时间已到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs38}死守我们的文化基地\N拉丁广场的火种\N坚决反对拆除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是传统的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位  朝这边看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅儿  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  都补好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的鲹鱼很便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  那晚饭就吃炸鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟外婆那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆  我是小海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没出现赤字很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是因为友子姐的工钱是外婆您亲自出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你就不用管了  就算咱们家不租客房她也是要来干活的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这些  小海  你还撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得辛苦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在一起热热闹闹的  我才不至于觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次看见你升起信号旗  我就觉得特别难过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是爱你父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天你能遇到个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你不用再升起信号旗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  那还真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  然后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一年级的女生说想成立个风间同学的粉丝团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:12:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可来电了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里卖电器的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢  小广
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女哟  你高高地升起信号旗  为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦拉几亚公国被夹在奥斯曼土耳其和俄罗斯之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:09.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拉丁广场周报\N用传统的飞跃抗议  为了拉丁广场的存续已有决死的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买的  30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30日元买这么一张照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易买的  我想找本人要个签名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去找风间同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人不敢去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢  我也没去过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:53.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35}守卫拉丁广场！！\N轻视传统谈何维新\N守卫拉丁广场  校内集会于5月15日\N为了保住广场大家团结一致！！\N不要让文化的火种熄灭！！\N坚决反对拆除拉丁广场！！\N反对拆除旧清凉庄\N让文化之馆拉丁广场留存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立宪制度下的政党在国民面前必须要重视自己言行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是到了政党内阁时代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当还是在野党的时候  在国民面前所声明的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦立于朝廷  就必定有将其赴以实行的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的黑子真是相当清晰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还排成一列
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人能感受到太阳的磁场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问「拉丁广场周报」编辑部怎么走？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三楼  考古研的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们立下了大大小小无数的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而仔细一看就能发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够称得上是他们政策的东西只有政策这个题目而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是空有形式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都不清扫的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野同学  考古研怎么走？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这上面  门口贴着文学社的牌子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  你们是来找我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的哲学学徒啊  我等你们等得好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待新部员的出现已经等了多少个岁月…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的辛苦果然没有白费
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去考古研和文学社的活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  别客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我跟你们讲一讲实存主义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是讲一讲尼采呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的化研  居然妨碍人家思考人生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  别站在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他抓住可要被迫听他的长篇大论咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！你们这些曲学阿世之徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天思考无法证实的空论的家伙有什么资格侮辱我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新时代的诗人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从云中从光中从暴风雨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得了透明的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向世人暗示人与地球应有的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新时代的哥白尼哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在是过于沉重…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！有感度了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is high school student from Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:57.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（文学社  拉丁广场周报编辑部）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山崎同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长  有稀客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临文学社  还是说…是来找考古研的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是来找非法刊物「拉丁广场」的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  水沼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来我们部岂不是废部了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您给我签个名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就给她签吧  英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是那个时候弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被猫抓伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你们谁来替俊刻板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里人手不够嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要忙学生会那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是她妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我叫松崎空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你帮他们刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我字写得可难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊  小空  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（木屐的物理卷  期中考试此处必考  命中率83%）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考试日益临近。在理科里称得上最难关的，应该算是过去无数学生含泪控诉的木屐出的物理试卷。然而大家无须担心。只要牢记本编辑部从大量的考试题中分析得出的结论，各位的担心就只是杞人忧天了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点有两个。仔细复习与加速度相关的部分，以及时刻注意木屐的陷阱。出题倾向最高的问题如下所示：
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢记以下公式！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度=初速度＋加速度×时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离=初速度×时间＋1/2×加速度×时间的平方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下问题必出！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水平光滑地面上，一台车正以一定速度作直线运动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 这种运动叫做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答：匀速直线运动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 当v=50cm/s时，求20秒后该车的速度和移动距离（不考虑空气阻力）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答：v=50cm/s时，设移动距离为s，则v0=500m/s，因为a=0
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据v=v0＋at得出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,v=50＋0×20
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, =50cm/s
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说速度不变！这是典型的陷阱
