Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是二年级？物理是那个木屐教的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是铃木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这东西就能派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是全校第一的水沼大人所做的精准考前预测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的17%就要靠自己的运气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就6点见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松崎同学  我护送你到出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被哲研那家伙缠住可就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这后面就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们只有行动才有出路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样坐下去等到废部的时候有什么脸去面对毕业的学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了  俊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松崎同学也一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来参加关乎拉丁广场存续的集会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刻好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  真是帮了我们大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集会！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广场的居民们  请迅速集合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集会！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  梅儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃咖喱  能帮我切一下蔬菜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.05,0:23:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.98,0:23:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还真晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小陆  能帮我去坡道下面买点东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去肉店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舟木一夫马上就出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前没让友子去买吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做便当用光了
